ency of AV node will get conducted. Thus the heart rate is very high without any pattern. (Here heart rate means ventricular rate)<\/p><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n","answer_id":27472,"question_id":19303,"up_vote_count":9,"last_edit_date":1420784827}],"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/questions/19303/what-does-irregular-heartbeat-mean-in-simple-language","last_activity_date":1455635997,"creation_date":1403679794,"answer_count":3,"title":"What does irregular heartbeat mean in simple language?","body":"<p>I bought a blood pressure monitor (A&amp;D UA-851) which has the option to measure irregular heartbeat.  I do understand what 'irregular' means, but why do irregular heartbeats happen and what are it's implications short and long term? <\/p>\n","question_id":19303,"tags":["cardiology","medicine"],"score":12,"accepted_answer_id":19304,"down_vote_count":0,"protected_date":1455636295,"is_answered":true,"view_count":2948,"up_vote_count":12,"last_edit_date":1403693643},{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/6b08f788d82ebc4c17318da09f7d98e0?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG","user_type":"registered","user_id":21920,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/21920/user21920","reputation":6,"display_name":"user21920"},"closed_date":1455641660,"comments":[{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/acb3c0063d438705f86396a8abc1b04a?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG&f=1","user_type":"registered","user_id":12877,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/12877/cmosychuk","reputation":4410,"display_name":"CMosychuk"},"score":0,"post_id":43392,"edited":false,"creation_date":1455635456,"comment_id":75107,"body":"<a href=\"http://structbio.vanderbilt.edu/sanders/Binding_Principles_2010.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow\">structbio.vanderbilt.edu/sanders/Binding_Principles_2010.pdf<\/a>"},{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://i.stack.imgur.com/SjvUL.png?s=128&g=1","user_type":"moderator","user_id":3340,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/3340/wysiwyg","reputation":23153,"di